 403:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_ll_utils.c ****   * @note   Function is based on the following formula:
 404:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_ll_utils.c ****   *         - PLL output frequency = (((HSE frequency / PLLM) * PLLN) / PLLP1 / PLLP2)
